technique and stuff like that.

180
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:20,250
I'll leave a link to his website.

181
00:07:20,250 --> 00:07:22,710
Actually, his YouTube
channel is brilliant too.

182
00:07:22,710 --> 00:07:24,510
There's a link to that in
the description as well.

183
00:07:24,510 --> 00:07:27,960
But anyway, as you can see,
I got part of the way there.

184
00:07:27,960 --> 00:07:30,720
The bits that stick out from
