How do you get from this to this?

198
00:08:00,060 --> 00:08:02,640
Well, this one was
created by Matthew Brand.

199
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:05,520
He really helped me to
understand what's going on,

200
00:08:05,520 --> 00:08:07,290
